title: [Teorainn Valley, Creek Trail]
description: The stone-filled creek rushes by, making a pleasant chuckling sound.  The path is barely illuminated by the moonlight filtering through the tall tanik trees.  Tanik needles line the path.
The stone-filled creek rushes by, making a pleasant chuckling sound.  The path is made cool by the tall tanik trees which filter the sunlight.  Tanik needles line the path.
